HEADWORD: Delate
<hw>De*late"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To dilate.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Goodwin.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Delation</ent>⟦br⟧
